{ Enteprise Service Bus #enterprise-bus-service

  The ESB is a specialized subsystem dedicated to communication to other subsystems.

  This approach allows to cut the interfaces between the systems. Thus, a subsystem can be exchanged with another subsystem more easliy because there are not many dependencies.

  Apparently also known as *horizontal integration*.


}
